# Project Overview

This is a service that converts Markdown content to beautiful images with API support, offering customizable themes and layouts.

## Key Files and Directories

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Package configuration and dependencies
- [src/pages/api/generatePoster.ts](mdc:src/pages/api/generatePoster.ts) - Main API for generating posters from markdown
- [src/pages/api/generatePosterImage.ts](mdc:src/pages/api/generatePosterImage.ts) - API for generating images directly
- [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx) - Main application page
- [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) - Main application layout

## Tech Stack

- Next.js for the frontend and API routes
- Puppeteer for rendering markdown to images
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Docker for deployment

